				<h3>Results</h3>

				<p>Results indicate that those who brainstormed and prototyped before receiving the narrow constraints yielded results that were both more novel and more appropriate than other groups. This research project at the 2013 <a href='http://uist.acm.org'>ACM Symposium on User Interface Software Technology (UIST)</a> in St. Andrews, Scotland. 
